President Muhammadu Buhari is currently attending the All Progressive Congress ( APC) virtual National Executive Committee at the Presidential Villa. The meeting kicked off at 12 noon . Vice President,Yemi Osinbajo and Secretary to the government of the federation, Boss Mustapha are also in attending the meeting . Senate President, Ahmed Lawan
And Speaker, House of Reps , Femi Gbajabiamila and principal officers of the National Assembly are in attendance. Also present at the meeting are the governors of Nasarawa , Niger , Jigawa, Pleateau , Imo, Kogi , Yobe , Gombe , Osun , Ogun and Lagos , Kwara, Kebbi, Kano and Ekiti . The court recognized chairman of the party, Victor Gaidom is also part of the meeting .